ZH: 我们需要隔离病毒感染者以控制疫情。
EN: We need to quarantine the infected individuals to control the outbreak.

ZH: 这个地区的人们正在接受自我隔离。
EN: The people in this region are undergoing self-isolation.

ZH: 学校已经决定实行隔离措施来保护学生安全。
EN: The school has decided to implement quarantine measures to ensure the safety of the students.

ZH: 他们被要求在家隔离14天。
EN: They were asked to isolate themselves at home for 14 days.

ZH: 隔离是最有效的方法之一来阻止疾病传播。
EN: Quarantine is one of the most effective methods to prevent the spread of diseases.

ZH: 在隔离期间，我们应该远离公共场所。
EN: During the quarantine period, we should stay away from public places.

ZH: 隔离可以帮助我们避免接触到病原体。
EN: Isolation can help us avoid exposure to pathogens.

ZH: 她被要求进行医学观察，以确定是否需要隔离。
EN: She was asked to undergo medical observation to determine if she needed to be quarantined.

ZH: 我们将组织专门的隔离区域来隔离疑似病例。
EN: We will set up dedicated isolation zones to quarantine suspected cases.

ZH: 隔离和隔绝是两个不同的概念。
EN: Quarantine and isolation are two different concepts.

ZH: 他们在隔离区内接受治疗。
EN: They are receiving treatment inside the isolation ward.

ZH: 隔离期间，我们需要保持良好的卫生习惯。
EN: During quarantine, we need to maintain good hygiene habits.

ZH: 隔离不仅仅是为了保护自己，也是为了保护他人。
EN: Quarantine is not just to protect ourselves but also to protect others.

ZH: 他们被隔离在医院的隔离室里。
EN: They are quarantined in the isolation room of the hospital.

ZH: 隔离措施对于早期发现和控制疾病扩散至关重要。
EN: Quarantine measures are crucial for early detection and control of the spread of diseases.

ZH: 隔离可能会导致心理压力，所以我们要关心隔离者的心理健康。
EN: Quarantine may lead to psychological stress, so we need to care for the mental health of those in isolation.

ZH: 隔离区内会提供必要的生活物资和医疗设施。
EN: The isolation zone will provide necessary supplies and medical facilities.

ZH: 不要亲自前往隔离区，以避免传播疾病。
EN: Do not personally visit the quarantine area to avoid spreading the disease.

ZH: 在隔离期间，我们可以通过电话或视频保持联系。
EN: During quarantine, we can stay in touch through phone calls or video communication.

ZH: 隔离是生病时的一种责任行为，以防止疾病蔓延。
EN: Quarantine is a responsible action when one is sick to prevent the spread of the disease.
